WEBVTT

00:22.256 --> 00:24.158
[DOOR CLOSING]

00:24.225 --> 00:26.960
Bless me, Father,
for I have sinned.

00:27.027 --> 00:31.132
How are you doing?

00:31.199 --> 00:33.801
It's been two weeks
since my last confession.

00:33.867 --> 00:37.538
I've done a lot of bad things
in that time.

00:37.605 --> 00:39.840
Didn't go to church,

00:39.907 --> 00:44.145
I took the Lord's name in vain
quite a few times,

00:44.212 --> 00:46.914
I cursed my mother-in-law,

00:46.980 --> 00:50.318
but it was in Italian,
so she couldn't understand,

00:50.384 --> 00:51.719
so I don't know
if that counts.

00:51.785 --> 00:52.820
It counts.

00:52.886 --> 00:54.522
Okay...

00:54.588 --> 00:57.591
And I cheated on my wife.

00:57.658 --> 00:59.927
You committed adultery?

00:59.993 --> 01:00.994
Yes.

01:01.061 --> 01:02.496
How many times?

01:03.964 --> 01:08.136
Five times the last two weeks.

01:08.202 --> 01:09.270
Wait...

01:09.337 --> 01:13.241
No, that's wrong.

01:13.307 --> 01:18.712
It was four times this week...

01:18.779 --> 01:21.115
with three women...

01:21.182 --> 01:24.685
and three times last week...

01:24.752 --> 01:26.287
with two other women.

01:26.354 --> 01:27.488
Wow.

01:27.555 --> 01:29.523
Plus, one of the women
from this week

01:29.590 --> 01:31.392
was the same as last week...

01:31.459 --> 01:34.528
or maybe two of the women
was the same,

01:34.595 --> 01:37.064
so I guess that makes...

01:37.131 --> 01:38.966
What? I don't know.
Seven times.

01:39.032 --> 01:42.336
I mean, it was more than
seven times, Father.

01:42.403 --> 01:47.107
It was more like 10 or 12
times, but, you know,
it was like...

01:47.175 --> 01:50.811
on seven different occasions,
only with five different
women,

01:50.878 --> 01:56.317
but some of the women
more than once...

01:57.851 --> 02:00.388
Some of them quite a
few times.

02:00.454 --> 02:02.923
In fact,
it's hard to say, Father.

02:02.990 --> 02:05.159
I didn't exactly keep count,

02:05.226 --> 02:08.496
but let's say a dozen times
in the last two weeks...

02:08.562 --> 02:10.698
