a pizza pie?

05:49.450 --> 05:51.218
Mom, it's a flower.

05:51.284 --> 05:52.720
Oh, I'm sorry.

05:55.556 --> 05:57.190
What do you think?

05:57.257 --> 05:59.226
Michelangelo.

05:59.292 --> 06:01.361
Look at that.

06:30.157 --> 06:33.827
Oh, the defenders of justice.
Hello.

06:38.098 --> 06:40.333
