all them 7-Elevens.

07:17.337 --> 07:18.539
You caught that guy?

07:18.606 --> 07:19.607
Right.

07:19.673 --> 07:20.974
Picked him up
last night.

07:21.041 --> 07:22.109
Thank God!

07:22.175 --> 07:22.976
You're doing
a great job.

07:23.043 --> 07:25.212
You hear that?

07:25.278 --> 07:28.148
That's how come, in America,
we live safe,
have a good life,

07:28.215 --> 07:30.150
because we've got cops like
Larry Schooner and
Carlos Wiley

07:30.217 --> 07:33.053
who make sure everybody
does what he's supposed to do.

07:33.120 --> 07:34.922
You work hard, pay taxes,
obey the law,

07:34.988 --> 07:37.825
you can have anything
you want.

07:37.891 --> 07:39.159
I want my kids to understand

07:39.226 --> 07:41.729
what a great country
we've got here.

07:41.795 --> 07:44.532
I think they understand.

08:04.084 --> 08:05.953
Hey, Rosalie,
keep your eye on the shop.

08:06.019 --> 08:07.855
