at Lacey Flynn's plumbing.

08:07.921 --> 08:10.290
Okay, sweetie.

08:10.357 --> 08:11.559
Her plumbing?

08:11.625 --> 08:12.793
Devo, when
you're done there,

08:12.860 --> 08:14.528
I want you to go
around back

08:14.595 --> 08:16.429
and clean out
the garbage cans.

08:16.496 --> 08:18.932
They're full
of maggots.

08:20.668 --> 08:24.304
Maggots. That's perfect.
I love that man.

08:24.371 --> 08:25.706
Don't worry.
I'll do it with you.

08:25.773 --> 08:28.241
