08:55.502 --> 08:56.837
See the way
she looks at him?

08:56.904 --> 08:58.706
That's not his fault.

08:58.772 --> 09:00.874
Besides, she's lonely.
I feel sorry for her.

09:00.941 --> 09:02.342
