for Joey.

09:04.444 --> 09:06.313
Hey, you shouldn't
talk like that.

09:06.379 --> 09:07.480
It's not right.

09:07.547 --> 09:09.049
Joey's my husband.

09:09.116 --> 09:11.484
I don't want
to see you get hurt.

09:11.551 --> 09:14.988
I can take care of myself.
Don't worry about me.

09:21.561 --> 09:23.030
