09:35.075 --> 09:37.510
Think she's pretty?

09:39.079 --> 09:40.614
Yeah, I guess so.

09:44.618 --> 09:46.019
I've got eyes, you know?

09:46.086 --> 09:47.888
I can see a lot of girls
are crazy for Joey,

09:47.955 --> 09:49.723
