for the ladies too.

09:49.790 --> 09:52.459
That's okay. He's Italian.
He's allowed to look.

09:52.525 --> 09:55.863
In reality as we know it,
some men do more than look.

09:55.929 --> 09:59.767
You don't trust anyone, Devo.
That's your whole trouble.

09:59.833 --> 10:01.068
