run around on me.

10:04.504 --> 10:05.538
Rosalie--

10:05.605 --> 10:06.674
He never would.

10:06.740 --> 10:07.975
Let me put it
this way.

10:08.041 --> 10:10.443
Let's say you had a dream
that he did,

10:10.510 --> 10:12.545
