14:30.403 --> 14:32.705
You reach in the bag
and take out a rune.

14:32.772 --> 14:34.107
Any one?

14:34.174 --> 14:37.244
Well, they're all
beautiful, you'll see.

14:37.310 --> 14:39.312
What are they, runes?

14:39.379 --> 14:42.182
They're stones.
They're very spiritual.

14:42.249 --> 14:43.350
