14:46.119 --> 14:48.155
Well, they tell you
where you're at.

14:48.221 --> 14:49.122
I'm at home.

14:49.189 --> 14:50.857
We're right here.

14:50.924 --> 14:51.959
What are you saying?

14:52.025 --> 14:53.393
No, spiritually.

14:53.460 --> 14:55.762
Spiritually, they tell you
where you're at.

14:55.828 --> 14:57.697
