or anything.

15:00.767 --> 15:03.636
Go ahead. Try it.
What can it hurt?

15:03.703 --> 15:05.338
Okay.

15:08.708 --> 15:11.711
Oh, this is a good one.
I love this one.

15:11.778 --> 15:13.380
This is strength.

15:13.446 --> 15:14.747
Strength?

15:14.814 --> 15:15.949
Yes.

15:16.016 --> 15:19.519
