Let me see.

15:40.473 --> 15:42.242
Sure it does. Look.

15:42.309 --> 15:43.810
Think I made that up?

15:43.876 --> 15:45.278
No, but I know you.

15:45.345 --> 15:46.613
I know what you think.

15:46.679 --> 15:49.216
JOEY: Rosalie, bring me
a beer, will you?

15:51.184 --> 15:53.120
