Because he refused

16:08.568 --> 16:10.470
to put the top back
on the mustard jar.

16:10.537 --> 16:12.805
Yeah, 27 times.

16:12.872 --> 16:14.741
Can you imagine?

16:14.807 --> 16:16.876
